'''Hanford Community Medical Center''' is located in the city of [[Hanford, California|Hanford]], [[California]]. Hanford Community Medical Center is a part of the [[Seventh-day Adventist Church|Seventh-day Adventist]] hospital system. Hanford Community Medical Center is part of a division of [[Adventist Health]] known as the "Adventist Health/Central Valley Network," consisting of Hanford Community Medical Center, [[Central Valley General Hospital]], [[Selma Community Hospital]], and seventeen Adventist Health/Community Care clinics throughout a {{convert|2500|sqmi|km2|adj=on}} region in the Central Valley.
